Procedure for running leaky tunnel:

1) Open 5 xterm windows and tile them
2) Set windows 1&2 to lcm_group1: 
   windows1&2: source lcm_group1.source
3) Set windows 3&4 to lcm_group2:
   windows3&4: source lcm_group2.source
4) Connect tunnel between windows 1&3
   window1: ./runTunnelServer.sh
   window3: ./runTunnelClient.sh
5) Setup listener in window 2:
   window2: ./listener
6) Turn on filter at 50kbps with 500ms delay
   window5: ./netem_filter.sh 50 500 0
7) Send 100 100kb messages
   window4: ./send_message 100 100000
8) Make sure to turn filter off when done
   window5: ./netem_filter_off.sh
